{"title":"菩萨蛮","authors":["沈其震"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":9,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"菩萨蛮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈其震"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中秋团圆佳节之夜，月明如昼，作此词遥寄台湾同胞并台湾当局。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平洋上风云亟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华儿女情尤急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咫尺是台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却伤行路难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何事夸功业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残败海棠叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请共补神州，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫教明月愁。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}